        <h2  >紫书的影评 &nbsp; &middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
        <span class="pl">( <a href="http://movie.douban.com/people/zishuzishu/reviews?cat_id=1002">26篇</a> )</span></h2>
        
        <div class="comment-item">
            <div class="pic">
